message.content: cs.HC, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CYBER, cs.SY - The paper deals with explanation generation for decision making agents in human-AI and human-robot interactions, which involves aspects of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), cybersecurity (cs.CYBER), and systems and control (cs.SY). The focus on evaluating these algorithms in a mock search and rescue scenario further supports the relevance of these sub-categories.
